---
title: Turkey, Bacon, Apple and Cheddar Melts with Wedges and Honey-Mustard Dip
description: Here's a sandwich that's sure to be a hit with the whole family! Sweet apples help to cut the richness from the bacon and cheese, while a side of BBQ-spiced wedges get honey-mustard mayo as a dunking buddy.
